    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine <strong>half</strong> the<strong> ras el hanout</strong> (save the rest for later!) in a bowl with the <strong>ground</strong> <strong>sumac </strong>and a generous grind of<strong> black pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>spice mix</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>halloumi </strong>and give it a good mix up to coat evenly– this is your <strong>spiced halloumi</strong></p>",
